Class TimezoneId

  • public class TimezoneId
extends TextProperty
    Defines a unique identifier for a VTimezone component. The identifier must be unique within the scope of the iCalendar object.
    Author:
    Michael Angstadt
    See Also:
    RFC 5545 p.102-3, RFC 2445 p.97-8
